,
									"text" : "You can change how color is mapped onto dk.plotter using the color messages. There are several available color maps as well as an optional offset to further alter the colors. As a rule of thumb linear offers the most accurate display and hsl offers the most visual contrast. You can also change the size depending on your UI requirements. You can also resize the UI to be small (169px), medium (235px), large (350px), or xl (600px). This can be set as an attribute or set dynamically."
